A '''Bat Wing''' is a type of [[Monster Loot]] dropped by [[Bats]] (any variant except for Iridium Bats) when slain. 10 bat wings can also be purchased for {{price|30}} each from [[Krobus]] on [[Days of the Week#Sunday|Sundays]].

The [[Desert Trader]] in [[The Desert|the Calico Desert]] will trade one [[Butterfly Hutch]] for 200 Bat Wings.

