==Tailoring==
Bat Wing is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the [[Tailoring|Dark Shirt]]. [[File:Shirt003.png|24px]]

==Quests==
*10 Bat Wings are requested by [[Void Salmon]] in a [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quest]] to increase the capacity of the pond from 3 to 5.
*10 Bat Wings may be requested by [[Catfish]] in a [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quest]] to increase the capacity of the pond from 5 to 7.

==History==
{{History|1.4|Can now be used in [[Tailoring]]. Can be requested in [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quests]].}}
{{History|1.5|Used as an ingredient in Monster Musk and Dark Sign recipes.}}

